Milton Kibbee https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milton_Kibbee 0 Milton Kibbee (January 27, 1896 – April 17, 1970) was an American film actor. He appeared in more than 360 films between 1933 and 1953. He was the brother of actor Guy Kibbee and his daughter was actress Lois Kibbee. Milton_Kibbee ( January_27_,_1896 – April_17_,_1970 ) was an_American_film_actor .
